result.name: 備長

reviews.text: 可能因為位置及價格關係，對環境及食物有一定期望，食物穩陣但抽風極需改善!!

有位女生的服務態度很好很熱情，應該是店長還是主管吧，食物的介紹也很詳細。建議提早預訂，這次6人聚餐，人均$280沒有包含飲料酒類，價位中等。
食物的份量不太好預算，有的一份有兩到三件、有的一份一件，要看清楚才下單🧐
最後有送上小點心 雪米糍:)
有機會會再度光顧~
很適合小型聚餐聊天喝一杯🍺
烤羊架和墨魚汁烏冬很驚喜！
串燒大多口味偏重。
關人隱士

result.name: Bicho 備長

reviews.text:
A place full of traditional Japanese decorations. Comfy interior design. Food is good with decent presentation. Grilled food sometimes are overcooked in my opinion.

Service is fair. Raised my hand for few times for filling the water but failed. Not really attentive. Price is in general higher than what it worths. Can give it a try but will not come back.

Worst dining experience ever, would not recommend anyone to go here . Waited more than an hour for the food . Food came so late. Everyone else got their food and they sat down after us.  Food quite standard. Super bad experience seriously . If there was a no star option , I would choose that , but in order to post this comment, I have to give a star .
Good
